inline_comments.message:
This doesn't check for valid characters, it only checks for uniqueness (the string format is to format the path query). It could be written more simply as:

    public boolean isUniqueSubscriptionId(final String subscriptionId) {
        return cpsQueryService.queryDataNodes(NCMP_DATASPACE_NAME,  SUBSCRIPTION_ANCHOR_NAME, 
                "//filter/subscribers[text()='" + subscriptionId + "']",
                FetchDescendantsOption.OMIT_DESCENDANTS).isEmpty();
    }
